race.comment: ROCKETS RED FLAIR (5) finished 3 lengths from the winner in fourth last start over 1207m at this track, an improvement on his fifth at Lone Star Park the run before. Best figures measure up nicely. Sure to run well. PERP WALK (4) has scored at his last two starts, most recently by 2.75 lengths over 1408m at this track (Dirt) as favourite. That continued the very strong form this campaign, with two wins from three starts. Big chance once again. HEY (3) scored two back at Prairie Meadows (Dirt) but was below his best last time when fifth over 1207m at Prairie Meadows (Dirt). Nicely placed to make amends. RISKY WITH WHISKEY (8) finished second two runs back at this track (Dirt) then improved last time out to score by 1.3 lengths over 1308m at this track (Dirt). Best figures measure up. Sure to run well. Something for the Multiples: DEVIOUS LOVER (6)
